reviews.text:
Wow! Yum! This smells and tastes fantastic!! Sweet strawberry, juicy apple, hint of watermelon, and just this exotic heady mouthful of yum!&#xD;
I can’t believe how good this is. This is my first strapon. The profile never interested me so I never bought or mixed one. This is seriously so delicious. I can taste the individual fruits if I force myself to think about them. But the magic here is how they all blend together into something delightfully sweet, fruity, and exotic. I don’t taste layers; I don’t taste the flavors in any particular order. I just get a single mouthful of wonderfulness! I am loving the Wood Spice in this. In nestles in perfectly with everything else. The watermelon is coming through a bit more now that everything is nice and warm. &#xD;
Great job!
